    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector condition. Powered by the S54B32 inline-six with individual throttle bodies, this unit features a documented rod bearing service and a structurally reinforced subframe. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmits power to a 3.62 limited-slip differential, ensuring peak mechanical engagement. With a pristine factory finish and zero-play suspension bushings, this example offers the precise turn-in and tactile feedback the chassis is heralded for. A mechanically flawless specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
