    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 BMW M4 in Alpine White, maintained to a standard that rivals a showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that gives it a deep, glass-like finish. Inside, the Sakhir Orange Merino leather remains supple and taut, with absolutely no wear on the bolsters and that signature new-car aroma still lingering. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; all services have been performed ahead of schedule at authorized BMW centers, with a comprehensive binder of records included. Every button, switch, and feature operates with factory precision. The forged 19-inch wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
