      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that rivals its original delivery state. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains entirely unblemished. Meticulously curated and preserved with the utmost care, this motorcar offers an uncompromising experience for the most discerning collector or enthusiast. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for excellence. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that defines showroom-quality distinction.",
      "price": 46500.0,
