    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this total gem. It is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it sparkling clean and perfectly maintained. It\u2019s been so reliable and runs like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person. Looking forward to chatting with you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
