    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This example boasts a comprehensive mechanical pedigree: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced for maximum torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains true to OEM specifications with refreshed bushings and a leak-free undercarriage. This is a turn-key performance icon, exhibiting perfect compression and a pristine interior for the discerning purist.",
